{
  "text": "Chhate ke andar se nikal kar bee bahar aati hai.
Phoolon ki khushbu se uska dil khush ho jata hai.
Spring ki roshni mein rang birange phool chamakte hain.
Bee har phool par uth kar mithas mehsoos karti hai.
Hawa ki naram lehron mein udte hue azaadi ka ehsaas hota hai.
Bee ke liye spring zindagi se bhara ek khoobsurat lamha hai."
}
